User Knows Desired Genre and Wants to see Sentiments:
This profile showcases a situation where a user knows what genre of movie they want to watch but want to see what sentiment people had about the movie.

Story:
A user logs into service. They want to watch an action movie but want to avoid one that will have scenes that evoke sad moods but donâ€™t specifically know what sentiment they want. User submit their desired genre and a list of movies are listed with the general sentiment and mood twitter users had about it. User can now pick a movie to watch.
